WEBVTT

00:04:59.861 --> 00:05:02.817
to the highest ideals.

00:05:02.817 --> 00:05:05.575
Orwell urged us to protect our language

00:05:05.575 --> 00:05:09.305
because ultimately our ability to think
and communicate clearly

00:05:09.305 --> 00:05:13.381
is what stands between us and a world
where war is peace

00:05:13.381 --> 00:05:15.919
and freedom is slavery.